    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h1 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-WelcometoServiceCentralDesk\">Welcome to ServiceCentral Desk</h1>\n<p>Your comprehensive guide to using the RepairQ platform. Browse by category below to find the help you need.</p>\n\n<hr/>\n\n<h2 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udcdaKnowledgeBaseCategories\">\ud83d\udcda Knowledge Base Categories</h2>\n\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"confluenceTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udcdaGettingStarted\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538138894\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udcda Getting Started</a></h3><p>Learn the basics of RepairQ</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83c\udfabTickets&amp;Repairs\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538433542\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83c\udfab Tickets &amp; Repairs</a></h3><p>Create and manage tickets</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udce6CatalogManagement\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538237128\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udce6 Catalog Management</a></h3><p>Manage your product catalog</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udccaInventoryManagement\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538237149\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udcca Inventory Management</a></h3><p>Track and manage inventory</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\uded2PurchaseOrders\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538204407\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\uded2 Purchase Orders</a></h3><p>POs, receiving, and RMAs</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udc65Customers&amp;Contacts\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538433565\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udc65 Customers &amp; Contacts</a></h3><p>Customer profiles and history</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udcb3Payments&amp;Devices\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4537549527\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udcb3 Payments &amp; Devices</a></h3><p>Payment processing and VCTs</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udcb0Pricing&amp;Taxes\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4537910056\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udcb0 Pricing &amp; Taxes</a></h3><p>Pricing, discounts, and taxes</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83e\uddfeInvoicing&amp;Refunds\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4537910077\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83e\uddfe Invoicing &amp; Refunds</a></h3><p>Invoices and billing</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udcc8Reports&amp;BI\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538302474\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udcc8 Reports &amp; BI</a></h3><p>Analytics and dashboards</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udda8\ufe0fPrinting&amp;Labels\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538302495\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udda8\ufe0f Printing &amp; Labels</a></h3><p>Printers and print settings</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udd14Notifications\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538302516\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udd14 Notifications</a></h3><p>Automated alerts and emails</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udcddCustomForms\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538138916\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udcdd Custom Forms</a></h3><p>Forms and signatures</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83c\udf10QsitePortal\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538171667\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83c\udf10 Qsite Portal</a></h3><p>Customer-facing portal</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udcf1QpopApp\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538204429\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udcf1 Qpop App</a></h3><p>Companion app</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udd17Integrations\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538204450\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udd17 Integrations</a></h3><p>APIs and webhooks</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udcbcAccounting\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538433586\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udcbc Accounting</a></h3><p>Journal entries and QB</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udc64Staff&amp;Locations\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538302538\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udc64 Staff &amp; Locations</a></h3><p>Staff management</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udcc5Appointments\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4537910099\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83d\udcc5 Appointments</a></h3><p>Scheduling and reminders</p></td>\n<td class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83c\udfa7HelpDesk\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4538270181\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83c\udfa7 Help Desk</a></h3><p>Support and troubleshooting</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"4\" class=\"confluenceTd\"><h3 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83c\udd95What&#39;sNew\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/4537910120\" rel=\"nofollow\">\ud83c\udd95 What's New</a></h3><p>Release notes and platform updates</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n\n<hr/>\n\n<h2 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udd0dQuickSearch\">\ud83d\udd0d Quick Search</h2>\n<p>Can't find what you're looking for? Use the search bar above or browse all articles alphabetically.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"ServiceCentralDesk-\ud83d\udcdeNeedHelp?\">\ud83d\udcde Need Help?</h2>\n<p>If you can't find the answer you're looking for, contact our support team.</p>",
